      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 for this factor, Gradation 1 (not assessed) is acceptable. The experimental dataset uses a single pump specimen representative of nominal manufacturing tolerances; sample-to-sample variability assessment is not required at this risk level."
    },
