    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion for the COU decision is supported by validated model predictions within the documented uncertainty bounds.",
